            , was indicted for that <rs id="t18090626-35-off203" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18090626-35-off203" type="offenceCategory" value="deception"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18090626-35-off203" type="offenceSubcategory" value="forgery"></interp>
               he on the <rs id="t18090626-35-cd204" type="crimeDate">9th of May</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18090626-35-off203 t18090626-35-cd204"></join>, feloniously did falsely make and caused to be falsely made and counterfeited, and willingly acted and assisted in feloniously forging a certain order for the payment of money, that is to say, for the payment of 47 l. 3 s. 6 d. with intention to defraud 
                     
                        <persName id="t18090626-35-victim428" type="victimName">
