               <p>Q. Look at that bill - A. This bill was shewn me at Queen-square, Westminster; it was not presented to me at Philpot-lane.</p>
               <p>Q. Are you acquainted with the hand writing of 
               <persName id="t18090626-35-person446">
                  William 
                  Morgan
               <interp inst="t18090626-35-person446" type="surname" value="Morgan"></interp>
