               <p>Q. Does it bear any resemblance to it - A. Not in any part of it.</p>
               <p>Q. Is it in part a printed check - A. Yes, one of our copper plate checks,</p>
               <p>Mr. Knapp. You say you know Mr. Morgan's hand writing, it is not in the least like it - A. I would not have paid it; it is not at all signed in the way he signs them. (The bill read.)</p>
               <p>"No. 17, Philpot-lane, 10th of May, 1809. Messrs. 
               <persName id="t18090626-35-person448">
