             and Co. Pay Mr. Haupins or Bearer, the Sum of Forty-seven Pounds, Three Shillings and Six-pence.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18090626-35-person449">
                  WILLIAM 
                  MORGAN
               <interp inst="t18090626-35-person449" type="surname" value="MORGAN"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18090626-35-person449" type="given" value="WILLIAM"></interp>
